24:02.000 --> 24:06.000
And the way we think about this is this is a fourth order problem in space.

24:06.000 --> 24:12.000
If I put this equal to 0, I have an ODE in four-dimensional phase space.

24:12.000 --> 24:16.000
And I can look at spatial eigenvalues of u equals 0.

