26:13.000 --> 26:16.000
because those spatial wave numbers have co-lessed

26:16.000 --> 26:20.000
and leaving you a multiple bifurcation in space,

26:20.000 --> 26:22.000
not in time, but in space.

26:22.000 --> 26:24.000
And the two solutions are these.

